and everything.

785
00:30:17,516 --> 00:30:19,283
Do I still get to rough him up
before the cops do?

786
00:30:19,285 --> 00:30:23,754
We'll be close by,
but technically, yeah.

787
00:30:23,756 --> 00:30:26,056
More in. You want
to know why?

788
00:30:26,058 --> 00:30:27,558
