796
00:30:40,873 --> 00:30:44,208
Because self-worth comes
from within, bitches.

797
00:30:44,210 --> 00:30:46,043
Now,

798
00:30:46,045 --> 00:30:48,779
if you'll excuse me,
(sighs)

799
00:30:48,781 --> 00:30:51,648
I need to slut this up.

800
00:31:00,693 --> 00:31:02,893
Oh, brother. Hello.

801
00:31:02,895 --> 00:31:05,896
