a little sting operation.

802
00:31:05,898 --> 00:31:07,464
(scoffs)
Right.

803
00:31:07,466 --> 00:31:10,133
I should've assumed
you'd be busy.

804
00:31:10,135 --> 00:31:11,635
I can come back.

805
00:31:11,637 --> 00:31:13,303
Well, no, no, that's
not a euphemism.

806
00:31:13,305 --> 00:31:17,641
I mean an actual police
sting operation.

807
00:31:17,643 --> 00:31:20,043
But actually, whilst
you're here...

808
00:31:20,045 --> 00:31:22,246
Here.

809
00:31:22,248 --> 00:31:25,215
Do you think I'm
boyfriend material?

810
00:31:25,217 --> 00:31:28,352
Luci, you've never exactly
been the type

811
00:31:28,354 --> 00:31:30,654
to get emotionally attached.

812
00:31:30,656 --> 00:31:31,688
To anyone.

813
00:31:31,690 --> 00:31:34,892
So I've come to
realize, but...

814
00:31:34,894 --> 00:31:36,994
what does that say
about me, brother?

815
00:31:37,830 --> 00:31:40,430
Is this about Chloe?

816
00:31:42,234 --> 00:31:45,702
And why would
you think that?

817
00:31:45,704 --> 00:31:49,172
Mom, she...
told me what happened

818
00:31:49,174 --> 00:31:51,308
or what almost happened,
apparently.

819
00:31:51,310 --> 00:31:52,609
Did she now?

820
00:31:52,611 --> 00:31:54,544
So, I suppose
you're gonna tell me

821
00:31:54,546 --> 00:31:56,280
humans and the divine don't mix.

822
00:31:56,282 --> 00:31:58,415
Luci, listen,
I have underestimated you

823
00:31:58,417 --> 00:31:59,616
for all of my existence,

824
00:31:59,618 --> 00:32:01,885
both in your ability
to frustrate me

825
00:32:01,887 --> 00:32:03,553
and your capacity for good.

826
00:32:03,555 --> 00:32:07,291
Even though you'll
never admit it, but...
(scoffs)

827
00:32:07,293 --> 00:32:10,227
when it comes to Chloe...

828
00:32:10,229 --> 00:32:12,396
perhaps you've been
underestimating yourself.

829
00:32:12,398 --> 00:32:16,333
Careful, brother. That sounds
dangerously like a compliment.

830
00:32:16,335 --> 00:32:17,601
Ah, take it how you like.

831
00:32:17,603 --> 00:32:19,870
You never listen
to my advice, anyway.

832
00:32:19,872 --> 00:32:22,005
Just one of
your many charms.

833
00:32:22,007 --> 00:32:23,473
Liar.

834
00:32:23,475 --> 00:32:25,842
But you're not, Luci.

835
00:32:25,844 --> 00:32:28,278
So, if you really
want to know

836
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:31,882
if you're a worthy
romantic partner...

837
00:32:31,884 --> 00:32:34,818
ask yourself.

838
00:32:36,588 --> 00:32:38,789
♪ ♪

839
00:32:44,964 --> 00:32:47,431
Can you guys hear me?

840
00:32:56,909 --> 00:32:58,208
Why are you
sitting so close?

841
00:32:58,210 --> 00:33:00,577
