Dan slept with Charlotte?

874
00:34:09,681 --> 00:34:12,482
Trust me, you're not half
as disgusted by that as I am.

875
00:34:12,484 --> 00:34:15,752
Is there anyone who hasn't slept
with that woman?

876
00:34:15,754 --> 00:34:16,887
Uh...

877
00:34:16,889 --> 00:34:18,255
Which is hard to believe

878
00:34:18,257 --> 00:34:20,290
since you've slept
with everyone else in L.A.

879
00:34:20,292 --> 00:34:21,892
Well, everyone except you,
Detective.

880
00:34:21,894 --> 00:34:23,260
I mean, not that I want to.

881
00:34:23,262 --> 00:34:25,128
I mean, of course
I want to, but...

882
00:34:25,130 --> 00:34:26,963
right now all
I'm concerned about

883
00:34:26,965 --> 00:34:28,832
is proving my worth to you.

884
00:34:28,834 --> 00:34:31,735
Unless of course you've
changed your mind about the sex.

885
00:34:31,737 --> 00:34:33,737
Okay, there will be no sex.

886
00:34:33,739 --> 00:34:35,539
As far as our so-called moment,

887
00:34:35,541 --> 00:34:37,941
I let my emotions get the best
of me the other night, okay?

888
00:34:37,943 --> 00:34:39,009
I made a mistake.

889
00:34:39,011 --> 00:34:42,112
You and me,
it's not happening.

890
00:34:42,114 --> 00:34:43,280
You have to accept, Lucifer,

891
00:34:43,282 --> 00:34:44,848
that we are
very different people

892
00:34:44,850 --> 00:34:46,349
with very different priorities.

893
00:34:46,351 --> 00:34:49,386
My priority right now
is this case.

894
00:34:49,388 --> 00:34:51,621
Okay? So, just...

895
00:34:51,623 --> 00:34:53,890
step outside and get some air.

896
00:34:53,892 --> 00:34:55,625
I don't need air.

897
00:34:55,627 --> 00:34:57,060
Well, I do.

898
00:34:59,364 --> 00:35:01,431
Right.

899
00:35:01,433 --> 00:35:02,799
Understood.

900
00:35:02,801 --> 00:35:05,001
♪ ♪

901
00:35:15,547 --> 00:35:17,547
(sighs)

902
00:35:22,788 --> 00:35:24,521
A man just entered the bar.

903
00:35:24,523 --> 00:35:27,224
Got you.

904
00:35:28,927 --> 00:35:30,727
You are one of the
prettiest flight attendants

905
00:35:30,729 --> 00:35:31,862
I've ever seen.

906
00:35:31,864 --> 00:35:33,530
Oh.
I'm Burt.

907
00:35:33,532 --> 00:35:35,532
Hi, Burt.

908
00:35:35,534 --> 00:35:37,501
You ready for takeoff?

909
00:35:38,537 --> 00:35:40,337
(chuckles)

910
00:35:40,339 --> 00:35:43,073
They're on their way
to the hotel room.

911
00:35:52,684 --> 00:35:55,285
Are you ready for the package?

912
00:35:55,287 --> 00:35:59,556
Mm-hmm. I think that's
supposed to be my line.

913
00:36:02,528 --> 00:36:04,027
I know you killed
that flight attendant

914
00:36:04,029 --> 00:36:05,829
and her friend, dirtbag.

915
00:36:05,831 --> 00:36:08,031
(grunts)

916
00:36:09,701 --> 00:36:11,101
No, no, no! My name's Jim!

917
00:36:11,103 --> 00:36:12,335
Some guy gave me a C-note,

918
00:36:12,337 --> 00:36:14,437
